        "f2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MORNING: Sun=EAST  → Shadow=WEST\nEVENING: Sun=WEST  → Shadow=EAST\nNOON:    Sun overhead → No shadow\n\nMorning + shadow LEFT  → face NORTH\nMorning + shadow RIGHT → face SOUTH\nEvening: all rules REVERSE",
      "autoResize": true,
