    {
      "id": "el_20",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 626,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Start facing North, walk 5km\nStep 2: No turns, straight line North\n\n       N\n       ↑ 5km\n       |\n     START\n\nTRICK:\nNo turn = direction stays same.\nDisplacement = distance in that direction.\n\nAnswer: 5 km North of starting point ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
