      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Start facing North, walk 5km\nStep 2: No turns, straight line North\n\n       N\n       ↑ 5km\n       |\n     START\n\nTRICK:\nNo turn = direction stays same.\nDisplacement = distance in that direction.\n\nAnswer: 5 km North of starting point ✓",
