    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1039,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 4km N then 3km E (right angle)\nStep 2: d = sqrt(3^2 + 4^2)\n     = sqrt(9+16) = sqrt(25)\n\n     FINAL\n    /|\n d / | 4km\n  /  |\n START--3km->\n\nTRICK:\nRight angle = Pythagoras! Check triplets.\n3,4,5 is a known triplet -> d = 5 km\n\nAnswer: 5 km from start ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 40,
      "isDeleted": false,
