      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 4km N then 3km E (right angle)\nStep 2: d = sqrt(3^2 + 4^2)\n     = sqrt(9+16) = sqrt(25)\n\n     FINAL\n    /|\n d / | 4km\n  /  |\n START--3km->\n\nTRICK:\nRight angle = Pythagoras! Check triplets.\n3,4,5 is a known triplet -> d = 5 km\n\nAnswer: 5 km from start ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
