      "y": 1023,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: x=+8(East), y=-6(South)\nStep 2: x>0, y<0 -> South-East quadrant\n\n  START---------\n  |              \\\n  6km S           \\\n  |                \\\n  +---8km E---FINAL\n\nTRICK:\nx sign + y sign -> quadrant:\nx>0,y>0=NE  x<0,y>0=NW\nx>0,y<0=SE  x<0,y<0=SW\n\nAnswer: SOUTH-EAST of start ✓",
