      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1371,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Two people start from the same point. Person A ends up at\nposition (4,3) and Person B at (8,1). What is the distance\nbetween A and B?",
      "fontSize": 13,
