      "x": 65,
      "y": 1798,
      "width": 787,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A person facing North makes 3 clockwise 90-degree turns\nfollowed by 1 anti-clockwise 90-degree turn. Which\ndirection is he now facing?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
