        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 3 CW from N: N->E->S->W\nStep 2: 1 CCW from W: W->S\n\nTRICK:\nNet turns = CW - CCW = 3-1 = 2 right turns\nN + 2 right = N->E->S\nEach 4 net turns = full circle (cancel)\n\nAnswer: Facing SOUTH ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
