    {
      "id": "el_70",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1895,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: N:+5y, R(E):+3x, R(S):-2y, L(E):+4x\nStep 2: x=3+4=7, y=5-2=3\nStep 3: d=sqrt(49+9)=sqrt(58)~7.62\n\n  A(0,5)--3E--B(3,5)\n  |            |\n  5N         2S\n  |            |\n  START  C(3,3)--4E--FINAL(7,3)\n\nTRICK:\nSum all x-moves and y-moves separately.\nApply Pythagoras on net (x, y).\n\nAnswer: ~7.62 km, NORTH-EAST ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
