      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: N:+5y, R(E):+3x, R(S):-2y, L(E):+4x\nStep 2: x=3+4=7, y=5-2=3\nStep 3: d=sqrt(49+9)=sqrt(58)~7.62\n\n  A(0,5)--3E--B(3,5)\n  |            |\n  5N         2S\n  |            |\n  START  C(3,3)--4E--FINAL(7,3)\n\nTRICK:\nSum all x-moves and y-moves separately.\nApply Pythagoras on net (x, y).\n\nAnswer: ~7.62 km, NORTH-EAST ✓",
