    {
      "id": "el_75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1895,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: S -> 90CW -> W\nStep 2: W -> 180 -> E\nStep 3: E -> 90CCW -> N\n\nTRICK:\nSum angles: +90+180-90 = +180 net CW\nS + 180 = N (opposite)\n180=opposite, 360=same, 90=next CW\n\nAnswer: Facing NORTH ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
